==Description==
'''Lanktir''' is a grobo living in [[Proxim-City]], next to the [[Proxim-City bazaar|bazaar]].

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
When [[Twinsen]] entered Lanktir's house, Lanktir gave him a [[keypad]] he recieved by accident. Twinsen was able to use it inside the [[Teleportation Center]].

When Twinsen was following the description of an old log of [[LeBorgne]] in order to find his treasure, he encountered a [[sphero]], who gave him a [[coffee pot]] he should return to Lanktir. When Twinsen did so, Lanktir gave him a [[list with clover boxes locations]].

